{"segment_id": "shijing__daya-wenwang-002__001__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "daya-wenwang-002", "source_id": "daya-wenwang-002__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 1, "canonical_ref": "詩經·大雅·文王之什·002.1", "text_original": "明明在下，赫赫在上。天難忱斯，不易維王。天位殷適，使不挾四方。", "text_normalized": "明明在下，赫赫在上。天難忱斯，不易維王。天位殷適，使不挾四方。", "notes": "大明 Chinese stanza 1."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__daya-wenwang-002__002__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "daya-wenwang-002", "source_id": "daya-wenwang-002__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 2, "canonical_ref": "詩經·大雅·文王之什·002.2", "text_original": "摯仲氏任，自彼殷商，來嫁于周。曰嬪于京，乃及王季，維德之行。大任有身，生此文王。", "text_normalized": "摯仲氏任，自彼殷商，來嫁于周。曰嬪于京，乃及王季，維德之行。大任有身，生此文王。", "notes": "大明 Chinese stanza 2."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__daya-wenwang-002__003__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "daya-wenwang-002", "source_id": "daya-wenwang-002__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 3, "canonical_ref": "詩經·大雅·文王之什·002.3", "text_original": "維此文王，小心翼翼。昭事上帝，聿懷多福。厥德不回，以受方國。", "text_normalized": "維此文王，小心翼翼。昭事上帝，聿懷多福。厥德不回，以受方國。", "notes": "大明 Chinese stanza 3."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__daya-wenwang-002__004__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "daya-wenwang-002", "source_id": "daya-wenwang-002__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 4, "canonical_ref": "詩經·大雅·文王之什·002.4", "text_original": "天監在下，有命既集。文王初載，天作之合。在洽之陽，在渭之涘。文王嘉止，大邦有子。", "text_normalized": "天監在下，有命既集。文王初載，天作之合。在洽之陽，在渭之涘。文王嘉止，大邦有子。", "notes": "大明 Chinese stanza 4."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__daya-wenwang-002__005__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "daya-wenwang-002", "source_id": "daya-wenwang-002__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 5, "canonical_ref": "詩經·大雅·文王之什·002.5", "text_original": "大邦有子，俔天之妹。文定厥祥，親迎于渭。造舟為梁，不顯其光。", "text_normalized": "大邦有子，俔天之妹。文定厥祥，親迎于渭。造舟為梁，不顯其光。", "notes": "大明 Chinese stanza 5."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__daya-wenwang-002__006__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "daya-wenwang-002", "source_id": "daya-wenwang-002__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 6, "canonical_ref": "詩經·大雅·文王之什·002.6", "text_original": "有命自天，命此文王。于周于京，纘女維莘。長子維行，篤生武王。保右命爾，燮伐大商。", "text_normalized": "有命自天，命此文王。于周于京，纘女維莘。長子維行，篤生武王。保右命爾，燮伐大商。", "notes": "大明 Chinese stanza 6."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__daya-wenwang-002__007__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "daya-wenwang-002", "source_id": "daya-wenwang-002__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 7, "canonical_ref": "詩經·大雅·文王之什·002.7", "text_original": "殷商之旅，其會如林。矢于牧野，維予侯興。上帝臨女，無貳爾心。", "text_normalized": "殷商之旅，其會如林。矢于牧野，維予侯興。上帝臨女，無貳爾心。", "notes": "大明 Chinese stanza 7."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__daya-wenwang-002__008__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "daya-wenwang-002", "source_id": "daya-wenwang-002__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 8, "canonical_ref": "詩經·大雅·文王之什·002.8", "text_original": "牧野洋洋，檀車煌煌，駟騵彭彭。維師尚父，時維鷹揚。涼彼武王，肆伐大商。會朝清明。", "text_normalized": "牧野洋洋，檀車煌煌，駟騵彭彭。維師尚父，時維鷹揚。涼彼武王，肆伐大商。會朝清明。", "notes": "大明 Chinese stanza 8."}
